<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #1B1B1B;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      padding-bottom: 24px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #E6E6E6;
    }
    .brand {
      color: #E55934;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #E55934;
      color: white;
      padding: 16px 32px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding-top: 24px;
      border-top: 1px solid #E6E6E6;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #757575;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div class="brand">YIMBY LA</div>
    <div>Red Tape Reporter</div>
  </div>

  <h1>Thanks for sharing your story!</h1>

  <p>We received your red tape report about your <%= @report.project_type.presence || "project" %>. Before we can review it, we need to verify that you're a real person (not a bot!).</p>

  <p>Please click the button below to verify your email and activate your report:</p>

  <div style="text-align: center;">
    <%= link_to "Verify My Report", @verification_url, class: "button", style: "background-color: #E55934; color: white; padding: 16px 32px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; display: inline-block;" %>
  </div>

  <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #757575;">Or copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
  <%= @verification_url %></p>

  <p><strong>What happens next?</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>We'll review your report</li>
    <li>Your story becomes part of our advocacy work</li>
    <li>We'll use this data to push for policy changes</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>Questions? Email us at hello@yimby-la.org</p>
    <p>YIMBY LA - Building a more abundant Los Angeles</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
